---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sectores — GeneraIA" description="El asistente de WhatsApp con IA se adapta a cualquier negocio: restaurantes, clínicas, peluquerías, tiendas y más.">
  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-50 bg-bg/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-border/50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="12" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          <text x="16" y="22" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="18" font-weight="700" font-family="Space Grotesk, sans-serif">G</text>
          <path d="M28 8 Q32 4 28 0" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.7"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight font-display">Genera<span class="text-accent">IA</span></span>
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm">
        <a href="/" class="text-muted hover:text-text transition">Inicio</a>
        <a href="/como-funciona" class="text-muted hover:text-text transition hidden sm:block">Cómo funciona</a>
        <a href="/sectores" class="text-accent font-medium">Sectores</a>
        <a href="/precios" class="text-muted hover:text-text transition hidden sm:block">Precios</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/34681072103?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20saber%20m%C3%A1s%20sobre%20GeneraIA" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="bg-accent text-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium text-sm hover:brightness-110 transition">Pruébalo gratis</a>
      </div>
      <button id="mobile-menu-btn" class="sm:hidden text-muted hover:text-text" aria-label="Menú">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"></line><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"></line></svg>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="mobile-menu" class="hidden sm:hidden border-t border-border bg-bg/95 backdrop-blur-xl">
      <div class="px-6 py-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <a href="/" class="text-muted hover:text-text transition">Inicio</a>
        <a href="/como-funciona" class="text-muted hover:text-text transition">Cómo funciona</a>
        <a href="/sectores" class="text-accent font-medium">Sectores</a>
        <a href="/precios" class="text-muted hover:text-text transition">Precios</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="pt-28 pb-16 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Sectores</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-muted text-center mb-16 max-w-xl mx-auto">El asistente se adapta a cualquier negocio. Cada uno tiene su configuración única — sin plantillas genéricas.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Restaurantes -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Restaurantes</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Gestiona reservas, responde preguntas sobre horarios, menú y alergias, todo sin que suene el teléfono.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Reservas automáticas por WhatsApp</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Captura de teléfono y número de comensales</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Atiende los lunes (cuando el local está cerrado)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Clínicas dentales -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Clínicas dentales</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Agenda citas, confirma asistencia y resuelve dudas sobre tratamientos sin que tu recepcionista se sature.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Citas automáticas sin llamadas telefónicas</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Recordatorio automático 24h antes</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Captura de leads para nuevos pacientes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Peluquerías -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Peluquerías y barberías</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Gestiona la agenda, evita los no-shows con recordatorios y capta nuevos clientes sin esfuerzo.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Reserva de citas sin llamadas</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Recordatorios automáticos (reduce no-shows un 70%)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Gestión de cambios de última hora</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Tiendas -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Tiendas y e-commerce</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Resuelve dudas de producto, stock y precios. No pierdas ventas porque el cliente se cansa de esperar.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Consultas de stock y precios en tiempo real</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Captura de leads con intención de compra</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Atención 24/7 fuera del horario comercial</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Talleres -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.066 2.573c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573 1.066c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066-2.573c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Talleres mecánicos</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Gestiona presupuestos, cita previa y consultas técnicas sin tener que parar de trabajar.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Presupuestos rápidos desde WhatsApp</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Cita previa sin llamar</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Captura de datos del cliente y del vehículo</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Asesorías -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Asesorías y gestorías</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Filtra consultas, capta nuevos clientes y responde dudas frecuentes sin saturar tu línea directa.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Responde dudas frecuentes sobre trámites</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Captura leads con datos del cliente y su caso</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">✓</span> Deriva a humano solo lo complejo</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <p class="text-muted mb-6">¿No ves tu sector? El asistente se adapta a cualquier negocio.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/34681072103?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20saber%20si%20GeneraIA%20funciona%20para%20mi%20negocio" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block bg-accent text-bg px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:brightness-110 transition shadow-lg shadow-accent/20">
        Pregúntame sin compromiso →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="border-t border-border py-8 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-muted">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="12" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          <text x="16" y="22" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="18" font-weight="700" font-family="Space Grotesk, sans-serif">G</text>
        </svg>
        <span>GeneraIA — 2026</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="mailto:hola@generaia.org" class="hover:text-text transition">hola@generaia.org</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/34681072103" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-text transition">WhatsApp</a>
        <a href="https://demo.generaia.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-text transition">Dashboard</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('mobile-menu-btn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.getElementById('mobile-menu')?.classList.toggle('hidden');
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
